    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698280/extras/1a11cc8f34e76788157b333c8e4450b0.poster.avif?t=1771003915\" width=1170 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698280/extras/1a11cc8f34e76788157b333c8e4450b0.webm?t=1771003915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698280/extras/1a11cc8f34e76788157b333c8e4450b0.mp4?t=1771003915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《CAPITALISM The action board game for one player》是一款融合卡牌机制的实时桌面游戏，你的目标是成为百万富翁。建立属于你的房地产帝国，在高风险的迷你游戏中争夺现金奖励，并且（希望如此）赚得比花得多。<br><br>策略与动作的结合，迷你游戏涵盖多种类型。街机经典、平台跳跃、弹幕射击等，应有尽有。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698280/extras/88733260af930604abeb40d7d5ac44e8.poster.avif?t=1771003915\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698280/extras/88733260af930604abeb40d7d5ac44e8.webm?t=1771003915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698280/extras/88733260af930604abeb40d7d5ac44e8.mp4?t=1771003915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>把你的 Microsoft Paint 放到一边吧：《CAPITALISM The action board game for one player》内置角色创建系统，让你可以设计出任何你能想象到的角色。通过专用代码格式，轻松保存、加载并与朋友分享角色。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698280/extras/6f50f13538f9d744c1d5179db3f93aa7.poster.avif?t=1771003915\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698280/extras/6f50f13538f9d744c1d5179db3f93aa7.webm?t=1771003915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698280/extras/6f50f13538f9d744c1d5179db3f93aa7.mp4?t=1771003915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在棋盘上策略性地放置卡牌，以优化你的收入。你能否用稳定的收入来源来抵消奢华的消费习惯？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698280/extras/a0e2ccb8dd4159c1ecbff3adad744bba.poster.avif?t=1771003915\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698280/extras/a0e2ccb8dd4159c1ecbff3adad744bba.webm?t=1771003915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698280/extras/a0e2ccb8dd4159c1ecbff3adad744bba.mp4?t=1771003915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>击败你的对手。偿还你的债务。你能掌握创造资本的艺术吗？你会如何花费你的100万元？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698280/extras/5defff04060a08b60118fb2d88524e53.poster.avif?t=1771003915\" width=1170 height=548 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698280/extras/5defff04060a08b60118fb2d88524e53.webm?t=1771003915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698280/extras/5defff04060a08b60118fb2d88524e53.mp4?t=1771003915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
